{"tid":349263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人唔食野唔訓唔飲水幾多日會死.....","createTime":"2017-08-06T12:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T12:58:47.000Z","uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"479f93f5ddcd356f469e277e1d4066790dfd5cd0","tid":349263,"uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"我個fd發燒百幾度 4日唔訓唔食唔飲水唔食藥 仲係咁自殘 拎隻手打張枱 又用個頭撞牆<br />\n佢屋企人又唔理佢<br />\n<br />\n佢同個男仔曖昧左一個月<br />\n佢地都鐘意大家<br />\n但條仔又話放唔低個ex乜乜柒柒<br />\n條仔又唔講清楚 係到拖拖拖<br />\n搞到我個fd 好唔開心好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n講極佢都唔聽<br />\n佢話佢好想訓 但一合埋眼就見到條仔纏住佢 想鍊死佢<br />\n食小小粥就嘔返出黎<br />\n<br />\n到底可以點幫佢<br />\n一日唔解開個心結<br />\n佢一日都係咁<br />\n <br />\n條仔真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未放低ex又溝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67273894956a58cc956e408ec131a7971f55734","tid":349263,"uid":14549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"有冇方法幫到佢"},{"pid":"cb47fa9ef87304885d23eb372cdda4c08235165d","tid":349263,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"捉佢入醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37a6810900357c76b1ae9e6b401f2530cf44be1","tid":349263,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:10:57.000Z","msg":"由佢"},{"pid":"43efea070ac2bcf090b693fd674593a4f6ea4166","tid":349263,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"幫佢報警 叫白車 有人暈左"}]}